    <assets>
        <TextAsset key="t_svalk622.00">
            <value key="en">What's this... ?</value>
        </TextAsset>
        <TextAsset key="t_svalk623.00">
            <value key="en">Hahaha! That was so much fun! I haven't been in a good battle in a long time.</value>
        </TextAsset>
        <TextAsset key="t_svalk624.00">
            <value key="en">Valkyrie...</value>
        </TextAsset>
        <TextAsset key="t_svalk624.01">
            <value key="en">I think I found it.</value>
        </TextAsset>
        <TextAsset key="t_svalk625.00">
            <value key="en">Found what?</value>
        </TextAsset>
        <TextAsset key="t_svalk626.00">
            <value key="en">(I take the item out of my pocket and show it to her. It's an elaborately worked key.)</value>
        </TextAsset>
        <TextAsset key="t_svalk627.00">
            <value key="en">O. M. G. This is...</value>
        </TextAsset>
        <TextAsset key="t_svalk628.00">
            <value key="en">(She was able to use the key.</value>
        </TextAsset>
        <TextAsset key="t_svalk628.01">
            <value key="en">It was kind of amazing.)</value>
        </TextAsset>
        <TextAsset key="t_svalk629.00">
            <value key="en">(She stuck it right into the face of the clock, and a keyhole appeared as thought it'd been there all along.)</value>
        </TextAsset>
        <TextAsset key="t_svalk630.00">
            <value key="en">(It all happened in broad daylight... Haha, that's just like her.)</value>
        </TextAsset>
        <TextAsset key="t_svalk631.00">
            <value key="en">(For a moment she went very still... I think she hesitated.</value>
        </TextAsset>
        <TextAsset key="t_svalk631.01">
            <value key="en">Then she turned the key, once, hard.)</value>
        </TextAsset>
        <TextAsset key="t_svalk632.00">
            <value key="en">(The thundercrack was so loud, it shook all of campus.</value>
        </TextAsset>
        <TextAsset key="t_svalk632.01">
            <value key="en">The light was yellow and soft and bright, like a hundred thousand fireflies flaring to life at once.)</value>
        </TextAsset>
        <TextAsset key="t_svalk633.00">
            <value key="en">(When I could see again... She was gone.)</value>
        </TextAsset>
        <TextAsset key="t_svalk634.00">
            <value key="en">It's been a few months since Valkyrie left. I still think about her.</value>
        </TextAsset>
        <TextAsset key="t_svalk634.01">
            <value key="en">A lot has happened since then.</value>
        </TextAsset>
        <TextAsset key="t_svalk634.02">
            <value key="en">Did I tell you? I'm dating someone now.</value>
        </TextAsset>
        <TextAsset key="t_svalk635.00">
            <value key="en">It's something I would have been too shy to do on my own...</value>
        </TextAsset>
        <TextAsset key="t_svalk635.01">
            <value key="en">Turns out, I learned a lot from her.</value>
        </TextAsset>
        <TextAsset key="t_svalk636.00">
            <value key="en">She left me a beautiful gift.</value>
        </TextAsset>
        <TextAsset key="t_svalk636.01">
            <value key="en">A sword that she made with her own hands.</value>
        </TextAsset>
        <TextAsset key="t_svalk636.02">
            <value key="en">Whenever I feel shy, I hold the sword and remember her.</value>
        </TextAsset>
        <TextAsset key="t_svalk636.03">
            <value key="en">I hope, wherever she is... She's found someone too.</value>
        </TextAsset>
        <TextAsset key="t_svalk637.00">
            <value key="en">It's been a few months since Valkyrie left. I still think about her.</value>
        </TextAsset>
        <TextAsset key="t_svalk637.01">
            <value key="en">I wonder how she's doing out there.</value>
        </TextAsset>
        <TextAsset key="t_svalk637.02">
            <value key="en">I hope she saved her people.</value>
        </TextAsset>
        <TextAsset key="t_svalk637.03">
            <value key="en">I definitely miss her. All I have left is my memories of her... And they become dimmer by the day.</value>
        </TextAsset>
    </assets>
